Special detective Kohachi Inugami is sent to investigate a grisly phenomenon involving animal corpses near a remote mountain village. But after meeting a strange boy who agrees to help, he discovers cursed supernatural forces at work. Little by little, Inugami uncovers the truth behind the killings and the boy who may not even be human.
(Source: Funimation)

Timid Tadano is a total wallflower, and thats just the way he likes it. But all that changes when he finds himself alone in a classroom on the first day of high school with the legendary Komi. He quickly realizes she isnt aloofshes just super awkward. Now hes made it his mission to help her on her quest to make 100 friends!
(Source: Viz Media)
Hokenshitsu no Otona na Senpai, Ore no Maede wa Sugu Dereru

Yuzuki, a senior member of the school infirmary committee, has a gentle and mature demeanor. Kyoji, a regular in the infirmary, got to know her as she teased him every day. He wanted to get back at her, so he said, "I like you..." When Yuzuki heard that, her behavior went haywire!?
(Source: Fantasia Bunko, translated)
Tobioriru Chokuzen no Doukyuusei ni "XXX Shiyou!" to Teian Shitemita.

My first love, her name is Koga Gumomo.

She was so much more beautiful and mature than a typical high school student, which attracted a great deal of jealousy and dislike. So much so that she was on the verge of jumping off the rooftop because of all the bullying she received.

So, what can I do to help?

"Why not have s*x with me!"
"............, you pervert! ...... (yuck!)"
"Maybe so! But are you sure? If you die here, your last memory will be the confession of some pervert you don't even know! It would ruin the mood!"
"............, what have you done! You pervert!"
"I have my reasons. Because I love you more than anything in the world! Let's get married!"
"What, ehhhh~~~............?"

I will yell out my love until I die, if it will make a place for you in this world!

The most stupid and straightforward protagonist in the history of romantic comedies and the cool, sullen JK will hook up for a romantic comedy with a sugar content of 100%!

(Source: Dengeki Bunko, translated)
